entries.journal_entry_description: After a simple search and rescue mission, Rebel Officer Acun Solari has had enough with the criminal element.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go out to a crashed Escape Pod
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You get ambushed by 4 Flail baddies
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Tell Acun Solari what happened to his friend.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Return and Talk to Acun Solari
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You have been rewarded with credits and Rebel faction for returning alive with news.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Kill 15 Flails on Corellia.  A location of one of their camps has been added to your datapad.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Kill Binayre Pirates on Talus and recover 10 of their gang symbols as proof.  A location to one of their common camps has been added to your datapad.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Once you have done as he asked, return to Acun Solari and talk to him.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Go into space and await further instructions.
entries.task08_journal_entry_title: Go into space to kill Hidden Daggers
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: You were rewarded for a successful mission.
